flowchart TD
    START[target] --> ID{id specified?}
    ID -- yes --> IDR[AXIdentifier match]
    ID -- no --> RL{role+label?}
    RL -- yes --> RLR[role+label match]
    RL -- no --> L{label?}
    L -- yes --> LR[exact label match]
    L -- no --> LM{label_matches?}
    LM -- yes --> LMR[regex label match]
    LM -- no --> TP{tree_path?}
    TP -- yes --> TPR[positional match]
    TP -- no --> PT{point?}
    PT -- yes --> PTR[screen coords]
    PT -- no --> ERR[spec parse error]

    IDR --> COUNT{matches}
    RLR --> COUNT
    LR --> COUNT
    LMR --> COUNT
    TPR --> COUNT
    PTR --> OK

    COUNT -- 0 --> RESOLVE_EMPTY[resolution_empty]
    COUNT -- 1 --> OK[resolved]
    COUNT -- >1 --> RESOLVE_AMBIG[resolution_ambiguous]
